headline: SWEP Introduces Brazed Heat Transfer Solutions Utilizing CO2-Reduced Steel
summary: SWEP, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a world-leading supplier of brazed plate heat exchangers (BPHEs), today announced the introduction of CO2-reduced steel as an option for customers seeking to minimize the carbon footprint of their heating systems and heat transfer projects.
